Package net.sf.jclec.syntaxtree

Syntax tree encoding package.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMutateSyntaxTree
    A single mutation operator for expression tree individuals
    IRecombineSyntaxTree
    Recombine an expression tree
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NonTerminalNode
    Non terminal node (containing a non-terminal symbol) in a syntax tree.
    SyntaxTree
    Syntax tree.
    SyntaxTreeCreator
    SyntaxTreeIndividual (and subclasses) creator.
    SyntaxTreeIndividual
    Syntax tree individual.
    SyntaxTreeIndividualSpecies
    Species for SyntaxTreeIndividual.
    SyntaxTreeMutator
    Abstract mutator for SyntaxTreeIndividual and its subclasses.
    SyntaxTreeMutatorTest
    Unit tests for all SyntaxTreeMutator subclasses
    SyntaxTreeNode
    Node in a syntax tree.
    SyntaxTreeRecombinator
    Recombinator for SyntaxTreeIndividuals and its subclasses.
    SyntaxTreeRecombinatorTest
    Unit tests for all SyntaxTreeRecombinator subclasses
    SyntaxTreeSchema
    Species for SyntaxTreeIndividual and its subclasses.
    SyntaxTreeSpecies
    ISyntaxTreeSpecies abstract implementation.
    TerminalNode
    Terminal node in a context-free grammar.
